Description: You were born to parents Oliver and Evelyn
Start infant school in Reception. Your parents chose Cape Coral technical school for you.
Move into Year 1 at infant school.
Move into year 2 at infant school. This is your last year there. Your parents are frantically trying to find a place at Junior school for you.
Start year 3 at Junior school. You make lots of friends very quickly. Your parents managed to find you a place at Lone Oak all-through.
Move into year 4 at Junior School.
Move into year 5 at Junior School.
Move into year 6 at Junior School. You have SATS exams at the end of this year.
Start year 7 at Secondary School. You don't make many friends to begin with. You are lucky enough to be attending Oceanside, without that persuasive letter your dad sent, this wouldn't have happned.
Oliver (your father) died due to being crushed by a stampede of hungry campers
Start yer 8 at Secondary School. You now have lots of friends..
Start year 11 at Secondary school. You have GCSE exams at the end of the year.
Start year 12 at College. Your parents wanted you to take English, Maths and Chemistry but you are taking Drama, music and Physics. You're now attending Sunset valley school.
